Yeah.

5
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:03,400
-Do you...
-All right, thanks.

6
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:10,080
Hi.

7
00:01:10,720 --> 00:01:12,360
Hey, Zion.

8
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:15,480
I am Eros,

9
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:16,840
your mum's...

10
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:19,040
her friend.

11
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:21,120
But she is not here.

12
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,440
