Wow, this is a very nice handshake.

14
00:01:29,080 --> 00:01:31,320
It's very firm. I like it.

15
00:01:31,320 --> 00:01:34,320
Thank you.
Uncle Joseph taught me that.

16
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,560
This is for you.

17
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:46,080
Thank you.

18
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:47,600
Do you want coffee?

19
