Hey.

54
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,120
He was here.

55
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:02,920
Who?

56
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:04,160
Eros.

57
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,000
What?

58
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:07,560
