to be a picture-perfect family,

134
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:52,480
so he can get a seat at the table.

135
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:54,280
And now...

136
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:56,000
And now, Joe is back.

137
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,880
You know, I always thought
I was on Team Joe.

138
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,200
But I'm not.

139
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:06,840
I'm on Team Jade.

140
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:09,480
