157
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,240
I can't wait

158
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:03,680
It's time to play

159
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:08,680
Darling better hold tight all night

160
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:11,800
Cause I ain't got other plans,
don't know about you

161
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:17,040
Yeah, this feels so right, alright

162
