So what does it take,
what does it take

163
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:22,320
I wanna beat your high score, yeah, yeah

164
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:24,000
Ring, ding, ding

165
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:28,720
Oh, yeah, yeah

166
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:35,200
Anyway, I'm so glad we are here
instead of the same old boardroom.

167
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:37,480
Yeah, can all their dinner meetings
be like this?

168
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:39,480
Eros is a genius.

169
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:42,880
Too bad
he isn't taking over Markos.

170
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:43,920
Isn't he?

171
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:46,040
But Mrs Lucas loves him.

172
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:48,480
I don't think the rest of them do.

173
