just like that

230
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:09,400
without fighting
until your very last shot.

231
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:10,960
You...

232
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:15,480
You are the most frustrating,
irritating and stubborn man

233
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:17,080
whom I have ever met.

234
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:20,560
But you have a heart
for your employees.

235
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:24,800
And I have no doubt
you will be a great CEO.

236
00:12:26,040 --> 00:12:28,800
Let's get you what you deserve
and get this over with.

237
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:32,080
Yeah. Okay.

238
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:34,960
You just had to attack me a bit, huh?

239
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,840
But before that...

240
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,520
Cheers.

241
00:12:49,680 --> 00:12:51,920
Let's go show them
what a spark looks like.

242
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:57,240
Ring, ding, ding

243
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:58,400
Go play a song.

244
00:12:58,400 --> 00:12:59,200
-What?
-Go play a song.

245
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,920
-Go, play a song.
-Go.

246
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:11,360
It's gonna be alright, you know

247
00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:16,720
It's gonna be alright, you know

248
00:13:17,560 --> 00:13:21,960
It's all gonna be alright, you know

249
00:13:23,040 --> 00:13:27,160
It's gonna be alright, you know

250
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:33,080
Let's do this together

251
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:36,680
Gonna get through this

252
