259
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:36,880
I'm sure he thinks
that he meant it,

260
00:14:36,880 --> 00:14:38,120
but he didn't.

261
00:14:38,880 --> 00:14:42,360
It's all about the business for him
and his guilt.

262
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:43,280
