00:15:21,680 --> 00:15:22,680
Oh.

274
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,400
Come on.

275
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,720
Are you okay?

276
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:54,840
You were a big part of my life, Joe.

277
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:57,960
And I think I depended on you

278
00:15:58,440 --> 00:15:59,840
too much.

279
00:16:02,920 --> 00:16:04,720
Even after you left,

280
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:07,400
you never really left my life.

281
00:16:07,400 --> 00:16:11,160
I allowed myself to be defined by you

282
00:16:11,800 --> 00:16:13,440
and your rejection.

283
00:16:14,480 --> 00:16:15,360
I didn't reject...

284
00:16:15,360 --> 00:16:16,360
I know that.

285
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:17,720
I know that now.

286
00:16:18,760 --> 00:16:21,240
And I can finally...

287
00:16:21,560 --> 00:16:23,080
breathe.

288
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:28,000
Knowing that you want me
feels like vindication.

289
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:33,640
And that's how I know this isn't love.

290
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:37,040
I can't...

291
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:42,680
I can't allow myself
to be defined by this anymore.

292
00:16:43,520 --> 00:16:45,160
I need to let you go,

293
00:16:45,560 --> 00:16:46,960
once and for all.

294
00:17:14,360 --> 00:17:15,840
You should go.

295
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:35,800
I heard you gave your approval?

296
00:17:35,800 --> 00:17:36,560
For?

297
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:38,720
Eros and that girl!

298
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:40,760
"Approval" is a strong word.

299
00:17:40,760 --> 00:17:42,320
Are you okay with it?

300
00:17:42,320 --> 00:17:44,680
With her becoming a part of our family?

301
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:45,640
Who told you anyway?

302
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:47,360
I have my sources.

303
00:17:47,360 --> 00:17:48,920
Yeah, Donovan.

304
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:50,120
You think she's a good fit?

305
00:17:50,120 --> 00:17:51,880
Well, like you said,
it's been a different Eros

306
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:53,480
ever since she came into the picture.

307
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:55,960
-If that's what it takes, so be it.
-Tell me something.

308
00:17:55,960 --> 00:18:01,720
If you really want Chloe to take over,
then why are you pushing him so hard?

309
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:03,880
It's just like your father pushed me.

310
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:08,200
He didn't just hand all of this to me.

311
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:11,080
I had to fight for it.
I had to earn his trust.

312
00:18:11,080 --> 00:18:13,280
Now, it's time for your son
to earn mine.

313
00:18:15,360 --> 00:18:16,360
What?

314
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:19,880
Well, it looks like he already has.

315
00:18:25,800 --> 00:18:28,000
Eros, I need to talk to you.

316
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:30,480
It's about Jade.

317
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:37,440
We will talk in the ring.

318
00:18:40,560 --> 00:18:43,120
Eros is Zion's father?

319
00:18:43,600 --> 00:18:44,720
Oh dear.

320
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:47,560
I thought these things
only happen in the movies.

321
00:18:47,560 --> 00:18:50,000
I wish someone would write me
a happy ending.

322
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:51,480
And what would that look like?

323
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:56,840
Me, the co-owner of a successful cafe,
reunited with the father of my child,

324
00:18:56,840 --> 00:18:59,480
and we all live happily ever after?

325
00:18:59,480 --> 00:19:01,360
Happily ever after?

326
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:03,360
Do you also believe in Santa Claus?

327
00:19:03,360 --> 00:19:05,600
I thought you were supposed
to make me feel better.

328
00:19:05,600 --> 00:19:06,920
Who has time for that?

329
00:19:06,920 --> 00:19:08,840
Besides, you didn't
just unload all this on me

330
00:19:08,840 --> 00:19:10,360
so I can make you feel better.

331
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:11,280
You did it

332
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:14,720
so that I can say
that you made the right decision.

333
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:17,240
Which I did, right?

334
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:21,040
You are a smart girl
with good instincts.

335
00:19:21,040 --> 00:19:22,480
But?

336
00:19:22,480 --> 00:19:26,720
But you took the easy way out,
and you pushed everybody away.

337
00:19:45,280 --> 00:19:46,760
What's your hold on Jade?

338
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:48,600
What do you mean?

339
00:19:49,160 --> 00:19:51,720
I don't think that
the two of you are in love.

340
00:19:51,720 --> 00:19:53,440
Or rather, that she loves you.

341
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:54,280
Why?

342
00:19:54,280 --> 00:19:55,800
-I know her.
-And?

343
00:19:55,800 --> 00:19:56,920
I kissed her.

344
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:01,880
You don't love him?

345
00:20:01,880 --> 00:20:03,480
No, I don't.

346
00:20:03,480 --> 00:20:05,920
Not anymore,
and that's what I don't get.

347
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:07,960
You are not the same Jade anymore.

348
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:10,040
You have evolved.
Feelings change.

349
00:20:10,040 --> 00:20:12,880
You may care about him,
but that's not the same as being in love.

350
00:20:13,280 --> 00:20:16,400
This Jade loves somebody else.

351
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:20,040
Should she love you,
she won't even allow me near her.

352
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:21,680
Really?

353
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:23,960
Do you really think
that you know Jade so well?

354
00:20:25,200 --> 00:20:28,400
Did you know that I love Jade?

355
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:31,400
Did you know that Zion is my son?

356
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:40,520
It's all just so complicated.

357
00:20:40,520 --> 00:20:42,600
No, it's not.
Steady the heart.

358
00:20:42,600 --> 00:20:44,320
Pay attention
to one feeling at a time,

359
00:20:44,320 --> 00:20:46,880
and also know that feelings
are not facts.

360
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,440
You need to weigh both.

361
00:20:48,440 --> 00:20:50,520
Then you will truly know yourself.

362
00:20:59,320 --> 00:21:00,800
You were punched in your face?

363
00:21:01,120 --> 00:21:02,040
Yeah.

364
00:21:02,040 --> 00:21:03,600
You should see the other guy.

365
00:21:05,040 --> 00:21:06,560
What's so urgent?

366
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:12,640
I'm grateful for the opportunity
that you've given me here, Uncle...

367
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:14,160
Mr Markos.

368
00:21:15,120 --> 00:21:16,960
Thank you for doing this for my dad,

369
00:21:16,960 --> 00:21:18,960
but I need to step down.

370
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:20,800
I can't continue working here.

371
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:22,240
Why?

372
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:25,280
I can't work with Eros.

373
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:29,720
I was expecting this sooner or earlier.

374
00:21:30,040 --> 00:21:30,920
But

375
00:21:31,320 --> 00:21:32,480
it's up to you.

376
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:35,080
If this is what you want,

377
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:36,840
so be it.

378
00:21:40,520 --> 00:21:42,600
There's something else
that I think you should know.

379
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:46,200
I owe you this, at least.

380
00:21:49,520 --> 00:21:51,680
Jade's child is your grandson.

381
00:21:58,400 --> 00:22:00,400
I have to go get Zion.
I'll see you tomorrow.

382
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:02,160
Can I say one more thing, though?

383
00:22:03,800 --> 00:22:06,800
As much as I love
your fierce independence,

384
00:22:06,800 --> 00:22:08,800
it's okay to need someone.

385
00:22:08,800 --> 00:22:10,680
I was exactly like you at your age.

386
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:13,000
I was so proud
to do everything on my own

387
00:22:13,600 --> 00:22:15,320
till I met my husband.

388
00:22:15,320 --> 00:22:18,280
He taught me that loving someone

389
00:22:18,280 --> 00:22:20,680
doesn't mean I have
to give up my independence.

390
00:22:21,120 --> 00:22:23,040
You must miss him a lot.

391
00:22:23,040 --> 00:22:24,520
Every day.

392
00:22:24,960 --> 00:22:26,680
I love you, Mrs Changley.

393
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:28,080
I love you too.

394
00:22:28,080 --> 00:22:29,760
Now go. Go get Zion.

395
00:22:30,360 --> 00:22:33,080
But make time to sit alone
with your heart,

396
00:22:33,480 --> 00:22:34,960
and pay attention.

397
00:22:35,360 --> 00:22:37,400
And weigh the facts and feelings.

398
00:22:37,400 --> 00:22:38,720
Yes.

399
00:23:08,200 --> 00:23:09,080
Eros.

400
00:23:09,080 --> 00:23:10,520
Something happened at the cafe.

401
00:23:10,520 --> 00:23:12,760
We should tell him about our arrangement.

402
00:23:12,760 --> 00:23:14,080
I love you, Jade.

403
00:23:17,520 --> 00:23:18,720
Eros Petrakis,

404
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:20,640
we need to bring you in for questioning.

405
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:21,880
